<br>
The main part of it was that a gnome was trying to make what he called the uberest firework in all of norrath. He needed certain components for his firework. And what you ask?<br>
<br>
The skin of Cazic Thule the god for the casing, and powder from Tolapumj. WTF? Stupid ass gnome im not doing my epic quest of firework creation! Gimme the damn stuff now.<br>
<br>
THAT was classic =)<br>
<br>
They changed it now and you go into PoF to try and repair a broken golem that beserks and you give him the oil that tells him his golem sucked and needed to die.<br>
<br>
