<br>
So what? These camps can all be done alone by a sufficiently high level monk (as far as I know). Ok the BK area camp in Chardok isnt that easy, but its not a rare drop there, I raided this area once and we got two monk drops in like four hours. Difficult? Not at all.<br>
<br>
If we could camp alone for all the stuff we need, I think no mage would complain, and if it took weeks. The problem is that we need raid forces for every damn TRY (Kedge, CoM, ...), only a few of our camps can be done with only one group.<br>
<br>
The real problem with the mage epic is not to convince your friends to help you once, but again...and again...and again...<br>
<br>
The worst thing so far I heard was someone fighting Phinny 76 times before he got his staff. Ok thats a bit extreme probably...but still, NO OTHER epic quest makes things so hard. This NEEDS to be changed.<br>
